==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enlimn
<hw>En*limn"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>limn</ets>. Cf. <er>Enlumine</er>,
<er>Illuminate</er>.]</ety> <def>To adorn by illuminating or ornamenting
with colored and decorated letters and figures, as a book or
manuscript.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Palsgrave.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

